	•	Individuals = atoms
	•	Relationships = bonds
	•	Groups = molecules
	•	Societies / nations / cultures = macromolecules
	•	Civilizations = molecular lattices
	•	History = chemistry playing out over time

This isn’t metaphor — this is literal emergent structure.

